Suppose We beed to add <code> tag .In order to beautify we will add this into custom CSS or code snippets



For White background
code {
   padding: 5px 5px 5px;
    border-radius:4px;
    background: #F2F2F2;
    font-size: 1em;
    line-height: 1.4em;
    color: black;
    border-style: solid;
    border-color: black;
    border-width: 1px;
}


For Black Background
code{
    padding: 0 5px 1px;
    border-color: #525252;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: #1B1B1B;
    font-size: 1.1em;
    line-height: 1.4em;
}
